Throwable(superclass of all exceptions & error)
Exception-(can be handled)
    -Checked exception
        -SQL Exception
        -I/O Exception
                -file not found
                -class not found

     -UnChecked Exception
     -Runtime exception
                -Arithmatic Excception
                -Null pointer exception
                -NumberFormat exception
                -IndexOutOfBound exception
                        -ArrayIndexOutOfBound exception
                        -String indexOutOfBound exception





error-(can not be handled)
        -stack overflow error
        -out og memory
        -unknown error